data.value: The 2018 Toyota Camry is a standout midsize sedan, featuring a 2.5-liter Dynamic Force 4-cylinder engine that generates 203 horsepower and 184 lb-ft of torque. Paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this sedan offers a smooth and efficient driving experience, achieving an impressive fuel economy of up to 29 mpg in the city and 41 mpg on the highway. The Camry's sleek design is complemented by 17" alloy wheels and LED headlights, while the interior boasts premium fabric-trimmed seats and a user-friendly Entune 3.0 infotainment system with a 7-inch touchscreen. Advanced safety features, including Toyota Safety Sense P (TSS-P) with Pre-Collision System and Lane Departure Alert, provide peace of mind on every journey. With a mileage of 32,000 miles and a price of $16,000, this 2018 Toyota Camry offers a blend of reliability, efficiency, and modern technology, making it an excellent choice for discerning drivers.
